                     <interp inst="t18431023-2962-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing, on the <rs id="t18431023-cd-109" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18431023-2962-offence-1 t18431023-cd-109"></join>25th of Sept</rs>., 60 pence; the monies of <persName id="t18431023-name-839" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18431023-name-839" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18431023-name-839" type="surname" value="PLUMMER"></interp>
